Package: conjest
Title: Basic conjoint estimands.
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: c(
    person("Lennart", "Kasserra", , "lennart.kasserra@uni-hamburg.de", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Alina", "Greiner-Filsinger", , "alina.greiner@uni-mannheim.de", role = c("aut", "ctb")),
    person("Max", "Schaub", , "max.schaub@uni-hamburg.de", role = c("aut", "ctb"))
)
Description: Provides tools for estimating and visualizing common estimands
    from conjoint survey experiments, including average marginal component
    effects (AMCEs) and marginal means (MMs), with support for
    cluster-robust standard errors and subgroup analyses. Implements the
    methods described in Hainmueller, Hopkins, and Yamamoto (2014)
    <doi:10.1093/pan/mpt024> and Leeper, Hobolt, and Tilley (2020)
    <doi:10.1017/pan.2019.30>.
License: use_mit_license()
Encoding: UTF-8
